{{TagLine|1200Mbps Wireless-AC Dual Band Repeater/AP/Router}} :{{ProductPage|http://www.pix-link.com/page50?product_id=146}} "LV-AC09-V1.1" and "2017.08.28" ais silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. *According to the [https://fccid.io/2AOQ6-LVAC09/Letter/Model-declaration-3762343 Model Difference Declaration] at the FCC, :"LV-AC09, LV-AC05, LV-AC06 [...] models are identical in the same :PCB layout, interior structure and electrical circuits. :The differences are color and model name for commercial purpose." The 5GHz Wi-Fi chip ID is not visible in the FCC photos and it's not obvious which :[[MediaTek]] chip this is based on from the 2x2 spec and MU-MIMO support. * Web GUI: http://mywifi.net
